OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773964972
OL,3,CCyprus weighs up the presence of
OL,4,CBritish troops after Iran missile
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FIt would be wrong to say the strike on
OL,8,FRAF Akrotiri in Cyprus ten days ago
OL,9,Fhas left Cypriots fearing for their
OL,10,Fsafety, but there is growing disquiet
OL,11,Fabout the presence of UK military
OL,12,Fbases on their island.
OL,14,F"It needs to be closed and then the
OL,15,Fisland will be safe," one Limassol
OL,16,Fresident tells us.
OL,18,FThere is a widespread view here that
OL,19,Fthe presence of RAF bases effectively
OL,20,Fputs a target on Cyprus.
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
