CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773964972
OL,3,CCyprus weighs up the presence of
OL,4,CBritish troops after Iran missile
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FThis week, newspapers here quote the
OL,8,FCypriot President Nikos
OL,9,FChristodoulides saying: "The presence
OL,10,Fof the British bases in Cyprus is a
OL,11,Fcolonial remnant. When this crisis is
OL,12,Fover we need to have a discussion with
OL,13,Fthe British government."
OL,15,FIt is a sentiment felt by people and
OL,16,Fby other leading politicians too.
OL,26,@qD@YOUuD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773964972
OL,3,CCyprus weighs up the presence of
OL,4,CBritish troops after Iran missile
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FNikolas Papadopoulos is the leader of
OL,8,Fthe Democratic Party; part of the
OL,9,Fcurrent governing coalition. He spoke
OL,10,Fto ITV News about why he thinks it is
OL,11,Ftime for the British to leave.
OL,13,F"We didn't choose to be in this
OL,14,Fstruggle, in this war, and yet we were
OL,15,Fattacked, inexcusably," he said.
OL,17,F"They have no place in a European
OL,18,Fmember state. But of course, things
OL,19,Faren't quite that simple. The UK has
OL,20,Fits own views that these bases serve
OL,21,Fall of our interests."
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@WO]yD@AOU}D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773964972
OL,3,CCyprus weighs up the presence of
OL,4,CBritish troops after Iran missile
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FI ask him what his view is and he is
OL,8,Fclear: "It is that they should leave
OL,9,Fand the Republic of Cyprus should be
OL,10,Ffree of any foreign troops."
OL,12,FThey were expecting the UK warship HMS
OL,13,FDragon to be close to Cyprus by now.
OL,15,FIt left Portsmouth earlier this month.
OL,16,FIt was filmed in Gibraltar earlier
OL,17,Fthis week and is still many miles from
OL,18,Fits destination.
OL,26,@pD@HOU
