OL,3,CCyprus weighs up the presence of
OL,4,CBritish troops after Iran missile
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FMeanwhile, Greek, French, Spanish and
OL,8,FDutch frigates patrol the Eastern
OL,9,FMediterranean.
OL,11,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FLast night, we met Stephen Doughty,
OL,17,FMinister for Europe, outside RAF
OL,18,FAkrotiri.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773964972
OL,3,CCyprus weighs up the presence of
OL,4,CBritish troops after Iran missile
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FI asked him if the original reason for
OL,8,Fhis visit was to coincide with the
OL,9,Farrival of HMS Dragon. He insisted
OL,10,Fthat this was an unrelated mission.
OL,12,FHe claimed that Cypriots do feel
OL,13,Fprotected by the presence of British
OL,14,Ftroops.
OL,16,FThere will not be any imminent
OL,17,Fdiscussion on the future of UK
OL,18,Fmilitary bases in Cyprus, but once
OL,19,Fthis conflict is over, whenever that
OL,20,Fmight be, people here want the British
OL,21,Fto hear them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773964972
OL,3,CCyprus weighs up the presence of
OL,4,CBritish troops after Iran missile
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FDoughty insists the base successfully
OL,8,Fprotects both British and Cypriot
OL,9,Finterests.
OL,11,F"I'm confident these bases are
OL,12,Fabsolutely secure, that they're
OL,13,Fcontributing to not only our security,
OL,14,Fbut the security of the wider region,
OL,15,Fand we are deepening our security
OL,16,Frelationship with our friends here in
OL,17,FCyprus," he said.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
