OL,3,CCyprus weighs up the presence of
OL,4,CBritish troops after Iran missile
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer has previously
OL,8,Fdescribed the level of cooperation
OL,9,Fbetween the British and Cypriot
OL,10,Fgovernment as "extremely positive."
OL,12,FIn the months ahead, it may need to be.
